The floor is heavily damaged from the sinking of earth under the foundation. The floor bends and sinks in many places, and much of the furniture here has toppled over as a result. You stand on the only intact portion of the floor near the west door.
You dig a small hole in the ground, but find nothing of interest and kick the dirt back in the hole.
An interesting but far-fetched proposition.
You pick through the remains on the ground.